    <item>
      <title>库马尔称拉丁裔选票对哈里斯来说至关重要</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-06/latino-vote-is-critical-for-harris-kumar-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拉美裔总统玛丽亚·特蕾莎·库马尔表示，美国需要明确的拉美政策。她还表示，拉美裔选民对卡玛拉·哈里斯来说至关重要。库马尔就“权力平衡”发表讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-06/latino-vote-is-critical-for-harris-kumar-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 00:16:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>热门 Netflix 节目 Judge 在餐厅上市后成为全球最富有的厨师之一</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/korean-gordon-ramsay-is-one-of-world-s-richest-chefs-on-restaurant-trading-debut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位韩国名人加入了全球最富有厨师的行列，他的餐厅特许经营权在周三首次交易时飙升 36%，他在该公司的股份价值约为 2.95 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/korean-gordon-ramsay-is-one-of-world-s-richest-chefs-on-restaurant-trading-debut</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 00:05:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员关注大选，比特币创一周最大涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/bitcoin-heads-into-us-election-count-with-biggest-jump-in-a-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着全球交易员关注美国总统大选结果的陆续出炉，比特币创下了一周来的最大涨幅，这场大选在数字资产支持者唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 与在政府打击该行业期间担任副总统的卡玛拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 之间展开。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/bitcoin-heads-into-us-election-count-with-biggest-jump-in-a-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 23:31:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价保持涨势，因交易员担心美国大选和飓风拉斐尔</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场关注美国总统大选结果，且飓风拉斐尔威胁墨西哥湾的生产，油价在连续五天上涨后趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 23:25:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国大选结果初显曙光，黄金价格保持稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/gold-holds-steady-before-results-of-coin-toss-us-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者密切关注可能对金融市场产生巨大影响的美国大选，黄金价格保持稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/gold-holds-steady-before-results-of-coin-toss-us-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 23:14:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥最高法院驳回限制司法改革的请求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/mexico-s-supreme-court-dismisses-bid-to-limit-judicial-overhaul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥最高法院驳回了旨在限制国会司法改革范围的裁决，缓解了人们对与总统克劳迪娅·辛鲍姆对峙可能引发宪法危机的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/mexico-s-supreme-court-dismisses-bid-to-limit-judicial-overhaul</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 23:09:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>选举之夜股市、美元和收益率上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股市延续涨势，美国国债收益率跃升，美元兑墨西哥比索和日元上涨，因为早期回报支撑了数月来随着唐纳德·特朗普的选举前景而上涨的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 23:05:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元贬值，日本股市因美国开始计票而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/japanese-stock-futures-edge-higher-before-us-votes-tallied</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员等待美国总统大选卡玛拉·哈里斯和唐纳德·特朗普之间的结果，日元走弱，而日本股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/japanese-stock-futures-edge-higher-before-us-votes-tallied</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 22:28:46 GMT</pubDate>
